## Run Tests

Run all tests:

```bash
cargo test
```

Run tests with output:

```bash
cargo test -- --nocapture
```

Run a specific test:

```bash
cargo test test_name
```

Run integration tests only:

```bash
cargo test --test lifecycle
cargo test --test search
cargo test --test mutation
```

